cn.campusapp.pan.lifecycle

接口 PanLifecyclePlugin


  • public interface PanLifecyclePlugin
    Just do something on proper lifecycle for every Activity/Fragment.
    It differs from ControllerLifecyclePlugin for it is only called once per lifecycle event.
    And it DOES NOT depend on the controllers to take effects.

    Created by nius on 12/18/15.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void onActivityLifecycle(android.app.Activity target, java.lang.Class<? extends LifecycleObserver> lifecycle, java.lang.Object... parameters)
      Called on every activity lifecycle for every activity controlled by Pan.
      void onFragmentLifecycle(android.app.Fragment target, java.lang.Class<? extends LifecycleObserver> lifecycle, java.lang.Object... parameters)
      Called on every fragment lifecycle for every fragment controller by Pan.

    • 方法详细资料

      • onActivityLifecycle

        void onActivityLifecycle(android.app.Activity target,
                         java.lang.Class<? extends LifecycleObserver> lifecycle,
                         java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Called on every activity lifecycle for every activity controlled by Pan.
        参数:
        target - target Activity
        lifecycle - e.g. OnResume
        parameters - the params passed by the system for that lifecycle

      • onFragmentLifecycle

        void onFragmentLifecycle(android.app.Fragment target,
                         java.lang.Class<? extends LifecycleObserver> lifecycle,
                         java.lang.Object... parameters)
        Called on every fragment lifecycle for every fragment controller by Pan.
        参数:
        target - target Fragment
        lifecycle - lifecycle e.g OnVisible
        parameters - the params passed by the system for that lifecycle
